3. When  will | enjoy  the rebate?
The bill rebates  shall be reflected  in your second  monthly  bill.
4. Who is eligible  for this postpaid  port-in  offer?

Customer  who ports in their postpaid  line to the CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G plans shown  below  during  the campaign  are eligible  for the postpaid  port-in  offer.
5, What  are the list of eligible  CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G Plans?

You can port-in  your postpaid  line to any of the following  CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G plans during  the promo  period  to enjoy  the RM20  monthly  commitment  fee
rebate  for 6 months.

6. Where  can| sign up for the CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G plans?

You may sign-up  via the CelcomDigi  website  here. Alternatively,  you may also walk into your nearest  CelcomDigi  Store,  Bluecube,  Digi Stores,  Celcom  and Digi
Dealers  to port-in  to the latest  CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G plans.
7. Does the RM20  x 6 months  rebates  comes  with contract?

No. Both the RM20  x 6 months  port-in  rebates  do not come  with contract.
8. Does the offer only applicable  if | sign-up  plan only?
The RM20  x 6 months  port-in  rebates  are applicable  for both for plan only or with device.

9, Can | enjoy  this offer together  with the RM10  x 12 months  contractual  rebates  for CelcomDigi  Postpaid  5G plan?
Yes. You can enjoy both Freedom  Add-Ons  rebates  and port-in  rebates.
10. What  will happen  to the rebates  if | change  my plan to another  plan?
The bill rebates  shall be forfeited  if there is downgrade  to non-eligible  plans.
